  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released on 9/1/2021 at 11:30pm CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.17.20-MinorChangesandImprovements\">Minor Changes and Improvements</h3><ul><li><p>Users with Admin priviliges can now update their company logos in Login, Navigation Bar, and Qsite Customer Portal with image file names that include spaces.</p></li><li><p>Reworked the Sales Summary by Staff export file to include all of the correct data for Percentage of Sales, Ticket Count, and Average Ticket Total columns.</p></li><li><p>Added the SKU column back to the Inventory Count page.</p></li><li><p>Added support for the PAX A80 payment device for use with the Bluefin integrated payment method.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.17.20-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Resolved an issue where Internet Explorer would not allow a user to create a new ticket.</p></li><li><p>The Compatibility modal now works on Internet Explorer.</p></li><li><p>Fixed the Edit Views modals on the Customers, Invoices, and RMA Tracking list view pages.</p></li><li><p>Using the restock fee feature no longer causes a negative balance erroneously after a ticket has already been closed.</p></li><li><p>Fixed a bug where the automatic clock out timer does not clock users out at the set time</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
